and are grateful to you.

32
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,660
Do you really think
you're a perfect man?

33
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,800
If your father weren't

34
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,030
the director of the police station,

35
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:03,900
do you think they would even
look at you?

36
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,780
Since we can't agree with each other,

37
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,620
let's talk on another day.

38
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,540
I'll ask you one last time.

39
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,000
Are you discarding

40
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,130
our friendship?

41
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,970
Will you just sink the opium

42
